## Getting Started (For Development / Forks)

```bash
# Clone
git clone https://github.com/RaineyMr/gradeflow.git
cd gradeflow

# Install
npm install

# Environment setup
cp .env.example .env.local
# Add: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, SUPABASE credentials, etc.

# Dev server
npm run dev
# Open http://localhost:5173

# Tests
npm test

# Deploy to Vercel
vercel deploy
```

